      "role": "user",
      "content": "whatever. i know the hotline thing. i've seen it a million times. it doesn't actually change the fact that people literally won't stop. it's like every time i look at my phone there's another person laughing at me or someone saying stuff that makes me feel like i don't even belong here. i'm just so tired of trying to defend myself. it feels like i'm losing a fight i can't even win.",
